channel.title: Suc My Diik - The new staker/pker on da block :P - lol funny name ay?
channel.description:
Well...This is how I got started with making this a funny name:
Last night (April 9, 2007), me and my bro(the one in the PM picture) was bored and started making up names about girls and stuff. So I got bored and ignored him and made a funny name (Hey bro...Sorry didnt tell ya I was bored of what you said, you talk to much...). I made an account called lick mi azz, suc mi ballz, tee bagger, etc...Lmao was really bored. Went around runescape with the account (the one below) and had a whole crowd following me lmao, if anyone has gotten banned for offensive names; I know a secret to not getting banned with them, but it requires boring things which is no talking. I tried reporting some dude called "Eat my pussi" and got banned for 2 days lol...Oh well, but you shouldnt talk mean to people if your going to have those kind of names. I'm thinking about sending a query to Mod Paul (Co owner of RS2), so that I can get my name verified so I dont get banned so easy. ANYWAYS! Keep laughing like those ones below and tell your story about your accounts being perm banned for offensive names lol...
Lol - Names on rs2 I pick own lol... [IMG]http://i13.tinypic.com/2s60z9i.jpg[/img]
